title: Looking for a support main ranked between Silver V and Gold I to try out.
body:
Hi all! My team and I are currently looking for a fifth and final piece, if you think you could help us out let me know by joining our discord channel.
We need a player who is willing to compete in the Summoners Society April Bronze to Gold  tournament, thanks all.

https://discord.gg/35h4teE
